There was no one above the water to slash at. Oh, and the missiles 
are spark signature seeking, not heat seeking. Fireballs wouldn't 
confuse them.

::Havoc/Demolition::

Demolition wakes up, looking around. He was floating toward an open 
cargo bay, being towed by Havoc.

Detatching himself from Havoc, he grabbs on to the pod, pulling it 
into the bay and dropping it there, the hatch closing behind them and 
the water filtering out.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
The Iron Fist continued to fire at Angel Prime.
